CustomField.description: This setting is used during ODRP(On Demand Response Push): If Checked, already associated Responses will also be considered for association along with the Orphan Responses. If Unchecked, only the Orphan Responses will be considered for the association.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: This setting is used during ODRP(On Demand Response Push): If Checked, already associated Responses will also be considered for association along with the Orphan Responses. If Unchecked, only the Orphan Responses will be considered for the association.
CustomField.label: Re-Associate Responses
